name: Taiga Aisaka LoRA [72MB]
description:
Taiga Aisaka LoRA from Toradora.

Primarily focused on getting the face accurate, but is able to get some of her outfits throughout the show. Easy to create images from the school age to post-graduation/adult (at least by presumption since the story becomes vague in the manga and the anime doesnt delve that far) by just altering obvious prompts that would be expected from aging...

Use a weighting of 0.7-0.8 and you should be fine, its very versatile.

Trained on Anything 4.0.

If you have any LoRA requests and wouldnt mind buying me a Hot Chocolate, please consider going to my page. https://www.buymeacoffee.com/JohnStinko
